WebAssembly with C++

Today's Focus: High-performance C++ in browser.
What I Learned:

Emscripten compilation

C++ to WASM

JS-WASM interop

Code:

cpp
// add.cpp
extern "C" {
    int add(int a, int b) {
        return a + b;
    }
}
// Terminal: emcc add.cpp -o add.js -s EXPORTED_FUNCTIONS="['_add']"

